<td style="width: 20px; vertical-align: top; border: none; color: #B2B7F2; font-size: 40px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, Times, serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: .6em; text-align: left; padding: 10px 10px;">“
</td>
<td style="vertical-align: top; border: none; padding: 4px 10px;">I cannot live without books.
</td>
<td style="width: 20px; vertical-align: bottom; border: none; color: #B2B7F2; font-size: 40px; font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;, Times, serif; font-weight: bold; line-height: .6em; text-align: right; padding: 10px 10px;">”
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="3" class="cquotecite" style="border: none; padding-right: 4%; font-size: smaller; line-height:normal; text-align: right;"><cite>—&#8202;<a href="/wiki/Thomas_Jefferson" title="Thomas Jefferson">Thomas Jefferson </a></cite>
</td></tr></tbody></table>
<div class="noprint" style="margin:0.3em 0.2em 0.2em 0.3em; padding:0.3em 0.2em 0.2em 0.3em; text-align:right;"><b><a href="/wiki/Portal:Books/Selected_quote" title="Portal:Books/Selected quote">More quotes</a></b></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div>
<div class="box-header-title-container flex-columns-noflex" style="clear:both;color:#600517;margin-bottom:0px;border:solid #600517;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;font-size:100%;background:#FCC200;font-family:sans-serif;padding:.1em;border-width:1px 1px 0;padding-top:.1em;padding-left:.1em;padding-right:.1em;padding-bottom:.1em;moz-border-radius:0;webkit-border-radius:0;border-radius:0"><div class="plainlinks noprint" style="float:right;margin-bottom:.1em;color:#600517;font-size:80%"><a class="external text" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Portal%3ABooks%2FDYK%2F6&amp;action=edit"><span style="color:#600517">edit</span></a>&#160;</div><h2 style="font-weight:bold;padding:0;margin:0;color:#600517;font-family:sans-serif;border:none;font-size:100%;padding-bottom:.1em"><span class="mw-headline" id="Did_you_know">Did you know</span></h2></div><div style="color:black;opacity:1;border:1px solid #600517;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;padding:1em;background:white;margin:0 0 10px;vertical-align:top;border-top-width:1px;padding-top:.3em;border-radius:0">
<div class="floatright"><a href="/wiki/File:Celsuslibrary-DK.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Celsuslibrary-DK.jpg" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cf/Celsuslibrary-DK.jpg/100px-Celsuslibrary-DK.jpg" decoding="async" width="100" height="115" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cf/Celsuslibrary-DK.jpg/150px-Celsuslibrary-DK.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cf/Celsuslibrary-DK.jpg/200px-Celsuslibrary-DK.jpg 2x" data-file-width="1395" data-file-height="1600" /></a></div>
<ul><li>...that <a href="/wiki/Celsus_Library" class="mw-redirect" title="Celsus Library">Celsus Library</a> was built in 135 A.D. and could house around 12,000 scrolls?<i>(Pictured)</i></li>
<li>...that following the advice of minister <a href="/wiki/Li_Si" title="Li Si">Li Si</a>, Emperor <a href="/wiki/Qin_Shi_Huang" title="Qin Shi Huang">Qin Shi Huang</a> ordered the burning of all philosophy books and history books from states other than <a href="/wiki/Qin_(state)" title="Qin (state)">Qin</a> — beginning in 213 BC?</li>
<li>...that according to the <a href="/wiki/Torah" title="Torah">Torah</a> in the fourth year of the reign of <a href="/wiki/Jehoiakim" title="Jehoiakim">King Jehoiakim</a> of Judah the prophet <a href="/wiki/Jeremiah_(prophet)" class="mw-redirect" title="Jeremiah (prophet)">Jeremiah</a> dictated the words of the Lord to Baruch, who wrote them in ink upon a roll of a book?</li></ul>
<div class="noprint" style="margin:0.3em 0.2em 0.2em 0.3em; padding:0.3em 0.2em 0.2em 0.3em; text-align:right;"><b><a href="/wiki/Portal:Books/DYK" title="Portal:Books/DYK">More Did you know facts</a></b></div><div style="clear:both;"></div></div>
<div class="box-header-title-container flex-columns-noflex" style="clear:both;color:#600517;margin-bottom:0px;border:solid #600517;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;font-size:100%;background:#FCC200;font-family:sans-serif;padding:.1em;border-width:1px 1px 0;padding-top:.1em;padding-left:.1em;padding-right:.1em;padding-bottom:.1em;moz-border-radius:0;webkit-border-radius:0;border-radius:0"><div class="plainlinks noprint" style="float:right;margin-bottom:.1em;color:#600517;font-size:80%"></div><h2 style="font-weight:bold;padding:0;margin:0;color:#600517;font-family:sans-serif;border:none;font-size:100%;padding-bottom:.1em"><span class="mw-headline" id="General_images">General images</span></h2></div><div style="color:black;opacity:1;border:1px solid #600517;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:left;padding:1em;background:white;margin:0 0 10px;vertical-align:top;border-top-width:1px;padding-top:.3em;border-radius:0">
